{
  "stem": "11723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was a very nice place, unlike where we were before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This happened to have been the mansion of the mayor of Buda, or the former mayor of Buda.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, he wasn't living there anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were over 100 kids living in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It had a gorgeous park around it, gorgeous park.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while it wasn't too cold we could go out there and play and have fun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as I said, we were 100 kids there, and a number of adults who were taking care of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now later I found out that all 100 of us were Jewish kids, but he thought that were the genuine article.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So things were kind of OK there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But every once in a while, a number of times a week, every week, the Nazis would come in to raid the place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Papers, papers, everybody's papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the two of us were supposed to have been the only authentic 'Aryans.' And each time the Nazis came they pushed my sister and myself in front and aren't they cute?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somehow we got away with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then one day a whole bunch of them came in and the women were desperate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought that this is it, this is it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister, who was really cute, I mean she was-- this is 1944, maybe November or so-- she was about two years old at the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She runs over to one of them and she says to him, hey, mister soldier, show me your cap.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the soldier picks her up and throws her In the air.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he looks at his companions and he says, only an Aryan child could be as cute as this one.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
